{"id": "art-2702b", "label": "Art. 2702b)", "title": "Art. 2702b)", "slug": "art-2702b", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1423367486\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1121\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1423367486\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 270<sup>2b)</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1088005425\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1120\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1088005425\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> europene\ncu sediul social în România au personalitate juridic&#259; de la data\nînmatricul&#259;rii în registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2122444529\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1119\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2122444529\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)O societate european&#259; nu poate fi\nînmatriculat&#259; în registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> decât\ndup&#259; încheierea unui acord privind implicarea <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\nîn activitatea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, în <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> prev&#259;zute de Hot&#259;rârea Guvernului\nnr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>187/2007</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_861998654\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1118\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_861998654\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În termen de 30 de zile de la înregistrare, Oficiul <span\nclass=SpellE>Na&#355;ional</span> al Registrului <span class=SpellE>Comer&#355;ului</span>\nva comunica Jurnalului Oficial al Uniunii Europene un <span class=SpellE>anun&#355;</span>\nprivind înmatricularea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>. <span\nclass=SpellE>Anun&#355;ul</span> va cuprinde <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute de art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>14</span><span\nstyle='color:black'> din Regulamentul Consiliului (CE) nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>2.157/2001</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>"}